title Srik_SPA NewNote Web Sequence

Browser -> Server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
note left of Browser: Browser sends post request to server
note right of Server: 
Response code 201 
Server does not redirect, stays on page
end note

note left of Browser: Browser loads css
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css
note left of Browser: Browser executes js code
Browser -> Server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa.js


note over Browser:
Browser starts executing js-code
that requests JSON data from server and 
updates the page with new note
end note
